446
00:30:14,270 --> 00:30:16,450
The second time I woke up,

447
00:30:16,450 --> 00:30:18,730
I thought it is a dream. The third time...

448
00:30:18,730 --> 00:30:20,520
Li Shiqing,

449
00:30:26,170 --> 00:30:28,020
Actually,

