611
00:40:39,690 --> 00:40:43,640
When he receives the watermelon, he has to share them with his coworkers anyways.

612
00:40:48,910 --> 00:40:52,000
- That's too big.
- Even though the watermelon might be crushed in pieces,

613
00:40:52,000 --> 00:40:55,120
