614
00:40:55,120 --> 00:40:56,940
Thank you.

615
00:40:56,940 --> 00:40:59,320
- Sir.
- I get some too?

616
00:40:59,320 --> 00:41:00,860
Wait, let me start filming.

617
00:41:00,860 --> 00:41:03,920
- Thank you so much.
